            "title": "仅含置位位的最小整数",
            "content": "#### 方法一：找规律\n\n**思路与算法**\n\n枚举仅包含置位位的整数： $1，3，7，15$。我们可以发现这个数列的规律，是前一个数乘以 $2$ 再加 $1$。\n\n首先我们初始化 $x = 1$，每次循环把当前 $x = x \\times 2 + 1$，循环一直进行，直到 $x$ 大于等于 $n$，返回结果。\n\n**代码**\n\n```C++ [sol1-C++]\nclass Solution {\npublic:\n    int smallestNumber(int n) {\n        int x = 1;\n        while (x < n) {\n            x = x * 2 + 1;\n        }\n        return x;\n    }\n};\n```\n\n```Java [sol1-Java]\nclass Solution {\n    public int smallestNumber(int n) {\n        int x = 1;\n        while (x < n) {\n            x = x * 2 + 1;\n        }\n        return x;\n    }\n}\n```\n\n```Python [sol1-Python3]\nclass Solution:\n    def smallestNumber(self, n: int) -> int:\n        x = 1\n        while x < n:\n            x = x * 2 + 1\n        return x\n```\n\n```JavaScript [sol1-JavaScript]\nvar smallestNumber = function(n) {\n    let x = 1;\n    while (x < n) {\n        x = x * 2 + 1;\n    }\n    return x;\n};\n```\n\n```TypeScript [sol1-TypeScript]\nfunction smallestNumber(n: number): number {\n    let x = 1;\n    while (x < n) {\n        x = x * 2 + 1;\n    }\n    return x;\n};\n```\n\n```Go [sol1-Go]\nfunc smallestNumber(n int) int {\n    x := 1\n    for x < n {\n        x = x*2 + 1\n    }\n    return x\n}\n```\n\n```C# [sol1-C#]\npublic class Solution {\n    public int SmallestNumber(int n) {\n        int x = 1;\n        while (x < n) {\n            x = x * 2 + 1;\n        }\n        return x;\n    }\n}\n```\n\n```C [sol1-C]\nint smallestNumber(int n) {\n    int x = 1;\n    while (x < n) {\n        x = x * 2 + 1;\n    }\n    return x;\n}\n```\n\n```Rust [sol1-Rust]\nimpl Solution {\n    pub fn smallest_number(n: i32) -> i32 {\n        let mut x = 1;\n        while x < n {\n            x = x * 2 + 1;\n        }\n        x\n    }\n}\n```\n\n\n**复杂度分析**\n\n- 时间复杂度：$O(\\log n)$。\n\n- 空间复杂度：$O(1)$。",
